Package treeNode

Class TreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • treeNode.TreeNode
  • public class TreeNode
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a node of the tree. It stores a letter, the frequency of the letter the files the letter is shown in, the child, next sibling and parent of the node.
    Author:
    Sundorius
